Package org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.bridge.json

JSON-protocol specific implementations of the interactions to IO-homecontrolled devices.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JsonBridgeCommunicationProtocol
    Common JSON-based bridge communication message scheme supported by the Velux bridge.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JCgetDeviceStatus
    Specific bridge communication message supported by the Velux bridge.
    JCgetDeviceStatus.Request
    Bridge I/O Request message used by JsonVeluxBridge for serializing.
    JCgetDeviceStatus.Response
    Bridge I/O Response message used by JsonVeluxBridge for deserializing with including component access methods Expected JSON (sample): { "token":"RHIKGlJyZhidI/JSK0a2RQ==", "result":true, "deviceStatus":"discovering", or "IDLE" "data":{}, "errors":[] }
    JCgetFirmware
    Specific bridge communication message supported by the Velux bridge.
    JCgetFirmware.BCfirmwareVersion
    Bridge Communication Structure containing the version of the firmware.
    JCgetFirmware.Request
    Bridge I/O Request message used by JsonVeluxBridge for serializing.
    JCgetFirmware.Response
    Bridge I/O Response message used by JsonVeluxBridge for deserializing with including component access methods Expected JSON (sample): { "token":"RHIKGlJyZhidI/JSK0a2RQ==", "result":true, "deviceStatus":"IDLE", "data":{"version":"0.1.1.0.41.0"}, "errors":[] }
    JCgetLANConfig
    Specific bridge communication message supported by the Velux bridge.
    JCgetLANConfig.BCLANConfig
    Bridge Communication Structure containing the network parameters.
    JCgetLANConfig.Request
    Bridge I/O Request message used by JsonVeluxBridge for serializing.
    JCgetLANConfig.Response
    Bridge I/O Response message used by JsonVeluxBridge for unmarshalling with including component access methods Expected JSON (sample): { "token":"RHIKGlJyZhidI/JSK0a2RQ==", "result":true, "deviceStatus":"IDLE", "data":"ipAddress":"192.168.45.9","subnetMask":"255.255.255.0","defaultGateway":"192.168.45.129","dhcp":false}, "errors":[] }

    JCgetProducts.Response
    Bridge I/O Response message used by VeluxBridge for deserialization with including component access methods Expected JSON (sample): { "token": "pESIc/9zDWa1CJR6hCDzLw==", "result": true, "deviceStatus": "IDLE", "data": [ { "name": "Bad", "category": "Window opener", "id": 0, "typeId": 4, "subtype": 1, "scenes": [ "V_DG_Window_Mitte_000", "V_DG_Window_Mitte_100" ] }, ], "errors": [] }
